# Connected bike event documentation

The following event types are send to the mqtt broker or possible to receive from the historic api.
The streaming events are always the latest versions. The historic data can have multiple versions of the events.

Please note, the contents and availability of events depend on the type of drive unit installed in the bicycle. Please have a look at the table [here](https://data-act.pon.bike/docs/connected-bike/).

